  "title": "Interior Design Intern",
  "description": "<p><strong>Role & Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Assist with drafting tasks and prepare technical drawings under guidance</li><li>3D/ Visualisation support</li><li>CAD Drawing support</li><li>Other relevant support duties to the design team across daily tasks, prioritising responsiveness, accuracy, and professionalism.</li><li>Weekly office upkeep</li></ul><p><strong>Qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Currently pursuing a Diploma/Degree in Interior Design, Architecture, or a related field</li><li>Proficient in AutoCAD, SketchUp, Enscape, Adobe Creative Suite etc.</li><li>Team player with collaborative work ethic</li><li>Keen eye for detail and ability to work under tight deadlines</li></ul><p>Candidates with portfolio/sample/school projects preferred. Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted for an interview.</p>",
